There's a possibility that he is already here, so let's secure the CCTV footage.

280
00:26:11,610 --> 00:26:13,160
Seonbae.

281
00:26:28,970 --> 00:26:32,550
Make it short.  I have to go out now.

282
00:26:33,750 --> 00:26:39,150
Do you know where the prosecution investigators who picked up Lee Jung Yeop are right now?

