287
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:55,540
At a Seoryun Hospital, too.

288
00:26:57,260 --> 00:26:59,650
You see it, right?

289
00:26:59,650 --> 00:27:02,710
Whose work of art this incident is.

290
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:11,110
Even Chief Bae could not have done this alone.

291
00:27:11,110 --> 00:27:16,220
This escape incident was fabricated by someone whom the police and prosecutor give a wide latitude of action.

292
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:19,110
You're talking about Seoryun, right?

293
00:27:19,110 --> 00:27:23,270
When deporting of Lee Jung Yeop would have been enough, why would Seoryun go this far?

294
00:27:23,270 --> 00:27:28,050
The Chimera incident of 35 years ago is not just a serial murder.

295
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:31,370
TH-5 is connected to it.

296
00:27:31,370 --> 00:27:34,760
A fraudulent patent application using fabricated research results.

297
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:38,860
That is our guess.  There's no way to prove it.

298
00:27:40,450 --> 00:27:42,460
No,

299
00:27:42,460 --> 00:27:44,730
I think they not only killed Lee Sang Wu

300
00:27:44,730 --> 00:27:47,840
but also Ryu Seong Hui too.

301
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:52,870
And right now, they are also trying to kill Lee Jung Yeop.

302
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:57,660
If you leave him on his own, he'll be in danger.

303
00:28:10,320 --> 00:28:14,250
Why are you so worried about him all of a sudden?

304
00:28:15,570 --> 00:28:21,770
You've always been overly interested in the chimera.  You also have far too much information

305
00:28:23,780 --> 00:28:25,970
and your source is confidential.

306
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:29,300
There is something I don't know, right?

307
00:28:30,210 --> 00:28:33,710
Do you have a personal grudge against Seoryun?

308
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:39,960
I do.

309
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:42,480
What's the reason?

310
00:28:44,050 --> 00:28:48,690
I ... am a murderer's daughter.

311
00:28:48,690 --> 00:28:50,140
What?

312
00:28:52,550 --> 00:28:57,350
I am the daughter of Lee Sang Wu, who died 35 years ago.

313
00:28:58,680 --> 00:29:00,660
What did you say?

314
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:02,230
That's right.

315
00:29:02,230 --> 00:29:07,700
The person who is being hunted right now, Lee Jung Yeop, is my oppa   (older brother) .

316
00:29:11,250 --> 00:29:13,900
That's ridiculous.

317
00:29:15,670 --> 00:29:20,640
Lee Sang Wu only had one child.  The only son was Lee Tae Yeong.

318
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:24,600
Again and again, you're trying to fool me.

319
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:40,550
When Lee Sang Wu died, his wife was nearly ready to give birth.

320
00:29:42,940 --> 00:29:45,660
How could she endure life

321
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:51,750
in the misery of the death of her husband and being pointed out as the family of a murderer?

322
00:29:53,540 --> 00:29:56,900
She died from a pulmonary embolism.

323
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:02,150
People took her corpse to the hospital,

324
00:30:02,150 --> 00:30:04,490
and the baby was resuscitated.

325
00:30:06,860 --> 00:30:09,910
The doctors cut open the dead woman's body

326
00:30:09,910 --> 00:30:12,200
and removed her infant.

327
00:30:15,090 --> 00:30:18,140
Some say it was a miracle.

328
00:30:19,020 --> 00:30:21,750
Others said it was grotesque.

329
00:30:26,730 --> 00:30:28,120
As for me ...

330
00:30:30,140 --> 00:30:32,290
on which side do you think I am?

331
00:30:43,450 --> 00:30:49,430
The dad I have now, took the child born under such tenuous circumstances and raised me.

332
00:30:51,310 --> 00:30:53,940
I didn't tell you about my dad, did I?

333
00:30:56,710 --> 00:30:59,300
Kim Hyeong Guk,

334
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:01,680
my dead dad's best friend,

335
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:03,790
and his lawyer back then.

336
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:06,270
His lawyer?

