Haven't you seen the movie, "The Fugitive"? The one with Harrison Ford?

352
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:53,940
His character's name in the movie is "Richard Kimble."

353
00:32:53,940 --> 00:32:57,720
A doctor who is falsely accused and hunted.

354
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:05,480
What time? Where is the show?

355
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:08,710
 Police

356
00:33:08,710 --> 00:33:12,210
Detective Cha, let me go with you.

357
00:33:13,670 --> 00:33:18,820
Reporter Kim, please wait. There will be a moment when I will need your help.

358
00:33:18,850 --> 00:33:23,240
Right now, we don't even know where the enemy is. If we move together, we are all exposed.

359
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:30,040
Please don't worry. I will bring him back.  Safely.

360
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:31,970
What if you can't?

361
00:33:33,830 --> 00:33:39,380
If you fail and something happens to him?

362
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:44,200
Your brother is not the only one

363
00:33:45,100 --> 00:33:47,870
fighting for his life.

364
00:33:50,450 --> 00:33:57,190
Trust me. It's different from 35 years ago.

365
00:34:00,620 --> 00:34:05,630
Only if the Chimera is caught,

366
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:12,070
and you are the one to catch him, will I then feel like it is true.

367
