368
00:35:45,370 --> 00:35:47,830
What's going on? Why are you here?

369
00:35:48,470 --> 00:35:52,860
Mom, He is strange.  He's being chased by a creditor.

370
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:57,100
Hey, in this world, is there anyone who doesn't have a story?

371
00:35:57,100 --> 00:35:59,920
Even so, he gets along just fine with Lee Yeong.

372
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:02,440
You don't even talk to Ji Yeong.

